SELECT COALESCE("t1"."POSTID", "t1"."POSTID") AS "POSTID", "t1"."TITLE", "t1"."CREATIONDATE", "t1"."VIEWCOUNT", "t1"."SCORE", "t1"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t1"."COMMENTCOUNT", "t1"."OWNERDISPLAYNAME", "t1"."UPVOTES", "t1"."DOWNVOTES", CASE WHEN "t3"."CLOSECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."CLOSECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "CLOSECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."REOPENCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."REOPENCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "REOPENCOUNT"
FROM (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Posts"."Id") AS "POSTID", "Posts"."Title" AS "TITLE", "Posts"."CreationDate" AS "CREATIONDATE", "Posts"."ViewCount" AS "VIEWCOUNT", "Posts"."Score" AS "SCORE", "Posts"."AnswerCount" AS "ANSWERCOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN "Comments"."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "COMMENTCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Votes"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "UPVOTES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Votes"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "DOWNVOTES", ANY_VALUE("Users"."DisplayName") AS "OWNERDISPLAYNAME"
FROM "STACK"."Posts"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Users" ON "Posts"."OwnerUserId" = "Users"."Id"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Votes" ON "Posts"."Id" = "Votes"."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Comments" ON "Posts"."Id" = "Comments"."PostId"
GROUP BY "Posts"."Id", "Posts"."Title", "Posts"."CreationDate", "Posts"."ViewCount", "Posts"."Score", "Posts"."AnswerCount", "Users"."DisplayName") AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostHistoryTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 10 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "CLOSECOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostHistoryTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 11 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "REOPENCOUNT"
FROM "STACK"."PostHistory"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t3" ON "t1"."POSTID" = "t3"."POSTID"